856
01:05:26,658 --> 01:05:29,360
Bosmu mengancamku.

857
01:05:32,852 --> 01:05:34,122
Halo?

858
01:05:34,122 --> 01:05:35,914
<i>Michael, orangku berhasil.</i>

859
01:05:35,916 --> 01:05:37,791
<i>Kau sebaiknya kemari
